01:01.887 --> 01:03.413
- Hey, Rick.
- Hey, Garrett.

01:03.438 --> 01:04.455
When'd you hit town?

01:04.498 --> 01:06.346
Came to see my kid.
I got to run, though.

01:06.383 --> 01:08.140
If I stick around, I'll call you.

01:08.463 --> 01:09.966
