31:53.488 --> 31:55.011
No, you want to come with us?

31:55.036 --> 31:56.559
I would, you know,

31:56.584 --> 31:59.533
if my favorite
movie character was, like,

31:59.612 --> 32:01.098
a plate of ground beef.

32:01.177 --> 32:03.019
But...

32:04.531 --> 32:06.921
Listen, are you in a hurry to get back?

32:07.221 --> 32:09.849
