32:17.398 --> 32:18.831
Hey, Tom.

32:20.445 --> 32:22.145
No, you're not.

32:23.028 --> 32:24.218
Who's that?

32:24.281 --> 32:25.780
He's a dick, pun intended.

32:25.858 --> 32:27.930
- He was a detective?
- Our only one.

32:27.983 --> 32:30.085
