32:52.794 --> 32:54.915
Sir, or should I say scumbag?

32:54.940 --> 32:56.475
- I prefer scumbag.
- Oh.

32:56.931 --> 32:58.280
- Peter, come on.
- Please follow me,

32:58.324 --> 33:00.527
